StatisticDescription:
The number of occurrences of the pattern 3241 or of the pattern 4231 in a permutation.

A permutation avoids these two pattern if and only if it is an ''input-restricted deques'', see [1].
StatisticTitle: The number of occurrences of the pattern 3241 or of the pattern 4231 in a permutation.
StatisticReferences: [1]  Pratt, V. R. Computing permutations with double-ended queues. Parallel stacks and parallel queues [[MathSciNet:0489115]]
